# @sonarsource/sonarqube-mcp-server-@@TARGET_ID@@

Platform-specific package for the SonarQube MCP Server on **@@TARGET_ID@@**. Do not install this package directly - install `@sonarsource/sonarqube-mcp-server` and your package manager will select the correct platform package automatically.

Contents:

- `jre/` - a jlink-stripped Temurin 21 runtime for this platform
- `sonarqube-mcp-server.jar` - the fat JAR of the MCP server
- `bin/sonar-context-augmentation[.exe]` - the context augmentation binary

See the main package for configuration and usage.
